---

interface Props {
  Lenguajes: string[];
  FrameworksBackends: string[];
}

const {
  Lenguajes,
  FrameworksBackends
} = Astro.props
---

<section id="experiencia" class="py-24 bg-blue-600 -mx-4 px-4 md:-mx-[max(2rem,calc((100vw-72rem)/2))] md:px-[max(2rem,calc((100vw-72rem)/2))] text-white overflow-hidden relative">
  
  <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 text-[20rem] font-black text-white/5 select-none leading-none -translate-y-20 translate-x-20">
    STACK
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10">
    <div class="mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.5em] text-blue-200 mb-4">Conocimientos T√©cnicos</h2>
      <h3 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-8xl font-black tracking-tighter leading-[0.9] uppercase wrap-break-word">
        Herramientas 
        <br class="block" /> 
        <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
          & <span class="text-black/30">Lenguajes</span>
        </span>
      </h3>
      <p class="mt-8 text-xl text-blue-100 max-w-2xl font-light">
        Mi ecosistema de desarrollo est√° dise√±ado para la escalabilidad.
        Desde arquitecturas Backend robustas hasta interfaces Fullstack interactivas
        (Construidas con ayuda de nuesta amiga la IA).
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-1">
      
      <div class="md:col-span-2 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md p-10 hover:bg-white/20 transition-all border border-white/10 group">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-12">
            <h4 class="text-2xl font-black uppercase italic tracking-tighter">Core Languages</h4>
            <span class="text-4xl group-hover:rotate-12 transition-transform">üöÄ</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          {Lenguajes.map((skill) => (
            <span class="px-6 py-3 bg-black text-white text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-blue-500 transition-colors cursor-default">
              {skill}
            </span>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-black p-10 border border-white/5 flex flex-col justify-between group">
        <h4 class="text-2xl font-black uppercase italic tracking-tighter mb-8">Backend Ecosystem</h4>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-sm font-bold text-blue-200/60 uppercase tracking-tighter">
          {FrameworksBackends.map((f) => (
            <p class="group-hover:text-white transition-colors text-blue-400">
              {f}
            </p>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white text-black p-10 flex flex-col justify-between group">
        <h4 class="text-2xl font-black uppercase italic tracking-tighter mb-8">Frontend & UI</h4>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            {['HTML5','CSS3','Angular', 'Astro', 'TailwindCSS'].map(s => (
                <span class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase border-2 border-black px-2 py-1">{s}</span>
            ))}
        </div>
        <p class="mt-8 text-xs font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase leading-tight italic">
            Creando interfaces que no solo se ven bien, sino que rinden al m√°ximo.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-2 bg-blue-900/50 backdrop-blur-sm p-10 border border-white/10 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center">
        <div class="md:w-1/3 text-center md:text-left">
            <h4 class="text-5xl font-black tracking-tighter uppercase italic leading-none">DB & <br/> MORE</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-2/3 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="space-y-1">
                <span class="text-blue-300 text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest">Database</span>
                <p class="font-bold uppercase text-sm">PostgreSQL / Mssql SQLServer / MongoDB / Redis</p>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-1">
                <span class="text-blue-300 text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest">TOOLS</span>
                <p class="font-bold uppercase text-sm">Docker / Git</p>
            </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-2 bg-blue-900/50 backdrop-blur-sm p-10 border border-white/10 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center">
        <div class="md:w-1/3 text-center md:text-left">
            <h4 class="text-5xl font-black tracking-tighter uppercase italic leading-none">DATA <br>BASES</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-2/3 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="space-y-1">
                <span class="text-blue-300 text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest">SQL</span>
                <p class="font-bold uppercase text-sm">PostgreSQL / SQLServer / MySQL</p>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-1">
                <span class="text-blue-300 text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest">NoSQL</span>
                <p class="font-bold uppercase text-sm">MongoDB / Redis</p>
            </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white text-black p-10 flex flex-col justify-between group">
        <h4 class="text-2xl font-black uppercase italic tracking-tighter mb-8">DevOps & Cloud / Web Servers</h4>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            {['Docker','Docker Compose', 'Nginx'].map(s => (
                <span class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase border-2 border-black px-2 py-1">{s}</span>
            ))}
        </div>
        <p class="mt-8 text-xs font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase leading-tight italic">
            Creando interfaces que no solo se ven bien, sino que rinden al m√°ximo.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-3 bg-linear-to-br from-gray-900 to-black p-10 border border-white/10 group overflow-hidden relative">
        <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between gap-12">
            
            <div class="md:w-1/4">
                <h4 class="text-3xl font-black uppercase italic tracking-tighter leading-none mb-4">
                    Dev <br /> <span class="text-blue-500">Tools</span>
                </h4>
                <p class="text-[10px] font-bold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest leading-tight">
                    El arsenal que garantiza la calidad y eficiencia del ciclo de desarrollo.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="md:w-3/4 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
                {[
                    {name: 'Git', desc: 'Version Control'},
                    {name: 'Postman', desc: 'API Testing'},
                    {name: 'Insomnia', desc: 'REST Client'},
                    {name: 'VS Code', desc: 'Main IDE'},
                    {name: 'DBeaver', desc: 'SQL Tool'},
                ].map(tool => (
                    <div class="group/tool cursor-default">
                        <span class="block text-white font-black text-sm uppercase tracking-tighter group-hover/tool:text-blue-500 transition-colors">
                            {tool.name}
                        </span>
                        <span class="block text-[9px] text-gray-600 font-bold uppercase italic tracking-widest">
                            {tool.desc}
                        </span>
                    </div>
                ))}
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="absolute right-0 bottom-0 opacity-[0.03] text-[8rem] font-black italic select-none pointer-events-none -mb-10">
              TOOLKIT
          </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>